The privileges and immunities of the civil service must not afford any single officer any measure of impunity in political adventure. Social media giant cites the risk of further violence following the assault on the US Capitol by his supporters During his four years in office, Trump used Twitter to ridicule his political opponents, labelling them with mocking nicknames. This comes after his repeated rejection of the election result and violent protests by his supporters.